							</div>
							<div class="exp-header-right">
								<div class="exp-period">Mar 2023 to Dec 2023</div>
								<div class="exp-toggle">
									<svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none">
										<path d="M5 1v8M1 5h8" stroke="var(--muted)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
									</svg>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="exp-body">
							<div class="exp-body-inner">
								<div class="exp-bullet">Prevented information silos during crisis response by creating a <b>consolidated dashboard</b> with projection and cross-system alerts.</div>
								<div class="exp-bullet">Improved anomaly detection speed and decision-making accuracy by identifying <b>3 design principles</b> through interviews with 23 NASA operators.</div>
								<div class="exp-bullet">Enabled instant parameter context without memory recall by designing an <b>annotated limit line system</b>.</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- FFVI -->
					<div class="exp-item">
						<div class="exp-header">
							<div class="exp-header-left">
								<div class="exp-company">Final Fantasy VI Worlds Collide</div>
								<div class="exp-role-line">
									<span class="exp-role">UX Designer, Lead</span>
									<span class="exp-type">Sponsored Project</span>
								</div>
								<div class="exp-summary">Led 8 designers to cut setup time by 75%, making a beloved 30-year-old game's complex randomizer accessible to a 10,000-person community.</div>
							</div>
							<div class="exp-header-right">
								<div class="exp-period">Jan 2023 to May 2023</div>
								<div class="exp-toggle">
									<svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none">
										<path d="M5 1v8M1 5h8" stroke="var(--muted)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
									</svg>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="exp-body">
							<div class="exp-body-inner">
								<div class="exp-bullet">Led a team of 8 designers to <b>reduce setup time by 75%</b> for novice players by redesigning the randomizer interface with a streamlined onboarding experience.</div>
								<div class="exp-bullet">Increased first-time completion rate by <b>40%</b> through a guided onboarding flow for complex game setup.</div>
								<div class="exp-bullet">Resolved the top 5 user complaints by rebuilding the settings panel with <b>progressive disclosure</b> and preset templates based on forum analysis.</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- PURDUE -->
					<div class="exp-item">
						<div class="exp-header">
							<div class="exp-header-left">
								<div class="exp-company">Purdue Sound Archive</div>
								<div class="exp-role-line">
									<span class="exp-role">UX Designer Intern</span>
									<span class="exp-type">Internship</span>
								</div>
								<div class="exp-summary">Built an interactive sound map with 100+ recordings connecting prospective students to campus life, reaching 10,000+ users.</div>
							</div>
							<div class="exp-header-right">
								<div class="exp-period">Jun 2023 to Mar 2024</div>
								<div class="exp-toggle">
									<svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none">
										<path d="M5 1v8M1 5h8" stroke="var(--muted)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
									</svg>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="exp-body">
							<div class="exp-body-inner">
								<div class="exp-bullet">Facilitated engagement for <b>10,000+ prospective students</b> with campus life by building an interactive sound map with 100+ recordings.</div>
								<div class="exp-bullet">Enhanced content discovery and reduced exploration time by developing a <b>responsive audio player</b> with location-based filtering.</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- EDUCATION -->
			<section class="section reveal" id="s-education">
				<div class="section-head">
					<span class="section-title">Education</span>
				</div>
				<div class="edu-grid">
					<div class="edu-card">
						<div class="edu-period">Aug 2024 – May 2026</div>
						<div class="edu-school">UC Berkeley</div>
						<div class="edu-degree">Master of Information Management and Systems<br><span class="edu-conc">HCI Concentration</span></div>
					</div>
					<div class="edu-card">
						<div class="edu-period">Aug 2021 – May 2024</div>
						<div class="edu-school">Purdue University</div>
						<div class="edu-degree">Bachelor of Science<br><span class="edu-conc">UX Design</span></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- SKILLS -->
			<section class="section reveal" id="s-skills">
				<div class="section-head">
					<span class="section-title">Skills</span>
				</div>
				<div class="skills-grid">
					<div class="skill-group">
						<div class="skill-group-label">Design</div>
						<div class="skill-group-title">Design and Strategy</div>
						<div class="skill-list">
							<div class="skill-item">UX / UI Design</div>
							<div class="skill-item">Interaction Design</div>
							<div class="skill-item">Information Architecture</div>
